== Project Info ==

post-mode has a new [http://post-mode.sourceforge.net home] and is now hosted on Sourceforge.  You can download it from the [http://sourceforge.net/projects/post-mode/ Sourceforge project site].

== Configuration ==

Extract post.el with <code>gunzip post.el.gz</code>. Put post.el in your load-path and add the following snipplet to your .emacs file:

 (require 'post)

== Documentation ==

A French howto was available but seems to have gone missing.  Please update this page if you know where it is.

Otherwise, all documentation can be found on [http://sourceforge.net/docman/?group_id=206008 the Sourceforge project site].

